# VEHICLE::DOES_VEHICLE_EXIST_WITH_DECORATOR

## Summary
Used to check for the existance of a vehicle with the specified decorator

## Parameters
* **STRING** decoratorLabel: Decorator label to check

## Returns
* **VEHICLE_INDEX**

## Description
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns whether a vehicle exists with the specified decorator
